<plot>Escaping a big argument with his wife, Chris winds up in the Scottish Highlands where he finds himself confronted with some perplexing architecture, and the equally puzzling Spencer: is he just a local with a sense of the absurd or, as he claims, an alien studying landscape features of the area? When Spencer suggests that where he comes from they have developed ways of connecting with each other that are far evolved from anything he knows, Chris's unease grows. But so does his curiosity; and they embark on an experience that may or may not be out of this world...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?594041</url></doc>
